,{"type":"b","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Designed Over 250 Gorgeous Courses","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":": Each course features spectacular scenery and fun shot strategies set over 26 themed locations across the globe\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"li","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"b","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"250+ Special Balls","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":": Special balls give players another layer of strategy for various course conditions\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"li","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"b","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Ongoing Live Events","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":": Fresh content keeps players engaged with over 150 Challenges, 125 Tournaments and 35 Kingdom seasons shared to date\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"li","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false},{"type":"b","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Over 17 Million Holes-in-One","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":": Giving players millions of reasons to celebrate\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":"\n","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"p","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"\n“We believe ","gated":false},{"type":"i","contentObject":[{"type":"text","content":"Golf Rival","gated":false}],"gated":false},{"type":"text","content":" has hit a hole-in-one with players because it appeals to both golf fans and casual gamers with a competitive, yet fantasy-driven golf experience,” said Henry You, StarLark Founder and General Manager. “We want to thank our players for the success we have achieved over the past four years and look forward to a